des:
Find contact info for B and O team members.

B and O Team Lookup can find the person you want to find easily.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Team Lookup" or "Alexa, open Team Lookup" to start your search".

At any time, you can stop the search by saying "Alexa, stop"
